'''羟嗪'''（{{pinyin|qiǎngqín (ㄑㄧㄤˇ  ㄑㄧㄣˊ)}}，{{lang-en|hydroxyzine}}，藥品名：'''安泰乐'''、'''維泰寧'''(Vistaril, hydroxyzine pamoate, capsule 25mg {{small|F631-15}})、Atarax）是属于[[二苯甲烷|二苯甲烷]]和[[哌嗪|哌嗪]]类的第一代抗组胺药。由于其可以与某些[[大脑|大脑]]中的受体结合，它被用作强力的抗[[焦虑症|焦虑]]药与轻度的抗[[强迫症|强迫症]]药，用来治疗精神上的焦虑与紧张。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=SCHRAM|first1=WS|title=Use of hydroxyzine in psychosis.|journal=Diseases of the Nervous System|date=March 1959|volume=20|issue=3|pages=126-9|pmid=13639831}}</ref>由于其有[[抗組織胺藥|抗组胺]]的效果，也可治疗严重的[[瘙痒|瘙痒]]，[[痛觉|痛觉]][[过敏|过敏]]和[[晕车|晕车]]引起的恶心，甚至作为缓解[[阿片戒断反应|阿片戒断反应]]的药物。<ref>FDA DrugInfo: http://dailymed.nlm.nih.gov/dailymed/archives/fdaDrugInfo.cfm?archiveid=51459 {{Wayback|url=http://dailymed.nlm.nih.gov/dailymed/archives/fdaDrugInfo.cfm?archiveid=51459 |date=20130617224511 }}</ref><ref name="urlHydroxyzine Facts and Comparisons at Drugs.com">{{cite web | url = http://www.drugs.com/cdi/hydroxyzine.html | title = Hydroxyzine Facts and Comparisons at Drugs.com | work =  | accessdate =  | archive-date = 2015-07-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150702210219/http://www.drugs.com/cdi/hydroxyzine.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>

